html:
Dec 3 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including AJ Bell, Rotork and Vestas, on Friday.


HIGHLIGHTS

* AJ Bell AJBA.L: Jefferies raises to hold from underperform

* Alfa Laval AB ALFA.ST: JP Morgan cuts to underweight from neutral

* Rotork Plc ROR.L: JP Morgan raises to overweight from neutral

* Vestas VWS.CO: JP Morgan cuts to underweight from neutral

* Wizz Air WIZZ.L: UBS raises to neutral from sell
